<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="py-3 px-3">
    <head>
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Remove Listing</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Remove Listing</h1>
        <p>
            Are you sure that you would like to remove "{{item_name}}"? <br>
            This is a permanent action and cannot be undone. <br>
            You will have to create the listing again if it is necessary again. <br>
        </p>
        <form method="post" action="/listing_removed">
            <input type = "hidden" name = "item_name" value = "{{item_name}}" />

            <input type="submit" value="Submit">
        </form><br>
        <a href="/">Or, return to the homepage</a>
    </body>
</html>